{"tid":1448212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:12.000Z","uid":205387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"979a53c7342e77763a40e88d6521cd14119f5767","tid":1448212,"uid":205387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=ed6faca7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=365441ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"ffdff04966b7361b2bb33e95e6a920885cc95afe","tid":1448212,"uid":205387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:07.000Z","msg":"自"},{"pid":"dd569bde8539531cfb013a5c0c72d853ed62d515","tid":1448212,"uid":205387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c46995c0b4ded4fc9f7957a8caa0aef1b0208097","tid":1448212,"uid":163236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=